Lighthearted Moment
⠀
I've noticed that the older I get, the more concerns and troubles start surrounding me. It's difficult to tell when exactly this happens, but for me it's getting harder and harder to stay as lighthearted as I used to be. I was contemplating this, and felt like telling a story which will let me involve the viewer in this contemplation.
⠀
The whole film was shot on Zhiyun Smooth-5 Gimbal @zhiyun_tech + Xiaomi 11T Pro @xiaomi.global
#Smooth5 #Gimbal #Mi11
⠀
And I hope it will give you some inspiration for your entries for the Mobile Film Challenge
#ZHIYUNMobileFilmChallenge
⠀
I would like to say thank you to @kk.english , @ikrents and @vitakrents for their help in creating this video.
⠀
Music: Waiting on the Sun by Kyle Cox
